{"serial": "13020", "department_serial": 14, "code": "FR2039", "class": "B", "name": {"en": "French Selected Readings II", "ch": "法文文選(二)"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": "本課程僅提供法文系同學修課，作為華語文學分學程課程抵修，非法文系同學請勿修此門課。"}, "instructor": {"en": ["Weng, Chen-Sheng"], "ch": ["翁振盛"]}, "credits": 2, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 3, "session": ["3", "4"]}, "loc": {"building": "C2", "room": "112"}}], "isRequired": true, "isFullSem": true, "MaxStu": 50, "department": {"ch": "法國語文學系", "en": "Department of French"}, "system": {"ch": "學士班", "en": "Undergraduate Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "國語", "en": "Chinese"}, "card": {"ch": "部份使用", "en": "Optional"}, "assigned": 2, "selected": 22, "remark": {"ch": "本課程僅提供法文系同學修課，作為華語文學分學程課程抵修，非法文系同學請勿修此門課。", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "在大一法文課程所奠定的基礎上，持續累積字彙，建立法文進階閱讀的基礎，進而培養文本的解析能力，使學生能夠在法文辭典的輔助下理解較為艱深的字句和文法，剖析文本的組織結構，解讀具備一定難度的文章和作品。", "en": "Aquerir la competence de comprehension de l’ecrit et une autonomie de l’etudiant face au foisonnement de textes en langue francaise."}, "outline": {"ch": "A組：\n延續大一法文文選課程，廣泛介紹各類型作品，上學期以青少年與兒童文學和童話故事為主，下學期以短篇小說為主。除艱難句意與文法結構的解析外，特別側重以下三個層面：文類特徵、修辭策略與敘述建構。\nB組：\n選文主要取自十九、二十世紀的法語文學文本。\n--上學期將選讀各類型文本，如抒情文、描寫文、敘事文、隨筆或雜感文、劇本，等名家作品選，以增進閱讀能力、充實詞彙、並經由文章多方接觸法國文化的各種面向。\n--下學期則以一個專題為中心，選不同作家的同主題文本，以進行主旨、書寫、觀點等各方面的文本分析和比較。", "en": "Travailler sur des textes litteraires de genres differents et de differents types ou autres pour que les etudiants en absorbent au fur et a mesure les structures, le lexique ou les modes d’expression.\nChaque texte termine par un debat."}, "textbook": {"ch": "1. DAUDET Alphonse, Lettres de mon moulin\n2. FLAUBERT Gustave, Dictionnaire des idees recues\n3. LA ROCHEFOUCAULD, Reflexions ou sentences et maximes morales \n4. LE CLEZIO Jean-Marie Gustave, Voyage au pays des arbres \n5. LEIRIS Michel, Nuits sans nuit et quelques jours sans jour\n6. MAUPASSANT Guy de, Mademoiselle Fifi \n7. PERRAULT Charles, Contes \n8. RENARD Jules, Poil de Carotte \n9. TOURNIER Michel, Pierrot ou les secrets de la nuit\n10. YOURCENAR Marguerite, Comment Wang-Fo fut sauve", "en": "1. DAUDET Alphonse, Lettres de mon moulin\n2. FLAUBERT Gustave, Dictionnaire des idees recues\n3. LA ROCHEFOUCAULD, Reflexions ou sentences et maximes morales \n4. LE CLEZIO Jean-Marie Gustave, Voyage au pays des arbres \n5. LEIRIS Michel, Nuits sans nuit et quelques jours sans jour\n6. MAUPASSANT Guy de, Mademoiselle Fifi \n7. PERRAULT Charles, Contes \n8. RENARD Jules, Poil de Carotte \n9. TOURNIER Michel, Pierrot ou les secrets de la nuit\n10. YOURCENAR Marguerite, Comment Wang-Fo fut sauve"}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "0", "en": "0"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授", "en": ["Lecture"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "課堂表現，期中考(口試)、期末考(筆試)。", "en": "Discussion and participation, mid-term exam, final exam"}, "officeHour": {"ch": "星期二第五、六節；星期三第五、六節", "en": "Tuesday 56; Wednesday 56"}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "18", "en": "18"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "domain": {"ch": "文學", "en": "文學"}, "map": {"ch": [{"competencies": "語言能力", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "口頭報告/口試", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "自學能力", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "口頭報告/口試", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "國際視野", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "口頭報告/口試", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "多元文化觀", "rating": "(1)非常低", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "口頭報告/口試", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "審美欣賞", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "口頭報告/口試", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "創意思考", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "口頭報告/口試", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "邏輯批判", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "口頭報告/口試", "出席/課堂表現"]}], "en": [{"competencies": "Competence in linguistic expression", "rating": "(4)High", "assesments": ["Test/Exam", "Presentation/Oral Exam", "Attendance/Performance"]}, {"competencies": "Autodidactic ability", "rating": "(4)High", "assesments": ["Test/Exam", "Presentation/Oral Exam", "Attendance/Performance"]}, {"competencies": "International vision", "rating":